            <h1 class="text-center">Imperial Pool <br /> Lifeguard</h1>
            <hr />
            <p>
                <b>Summers 2017 - 2019</b>
                <br /><br />
                During his job as a lifeguard, Kalen spent most of my time supervising swimming. In the other time, he manned the cash register
                selling memberships, snacks, and drinks. Outside of public hours, he taught swimming lessons and cleaned the facility.
            </p>
